\]

Using \(\hbar = 1.054571817\times10^{-34}\,\text{J·s}\),

\[
\Delta p \approx \frac{\hbar}{2\Delta x}
          = \frac{1.054571817\times10^{-34}}{2(1.058\times10^{-10})}
          \approx 4.99\times10^{-25}\ \text{kg·m/s}
\]

Rounded to a convenient significant figure:

\[
